overview: A village girl named Sean who was educated barbarically by her mother. He does not know who his biological father is so he feels he is an "illegitimate child". Sean couldn't believe it. Sean wants to try to be a better girl when he is loved by Amri, a city man who is the son of a transgender man. When Sean begins to love Amri, it turns out that the man of his dreams is already engaged.
title: Cintanya Cewek Barbar
